  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/7f26ea1c17cf272e2961c7f00400b3f4.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immerse</strong> yourself in a <u><strong>fortress building simulator</strong></u> with elements of <u><strong>turn-based strategy</strong></u> and <u><strong>real-time strategy</strong></u> in our new game Tiny Europe! <br> <br><strong>Dark forces do not sleep!</strong> You have miraculously survived on the bizarre continent of Europe, but this is just the beginning. You have to build a fortress in <u><i>60 seconds</i></u>, until the first enemy attack begins. Everything you manage to build in <u><i>60 seconds</i></u> will be free for you. After <u><i>60 seconds</i></u> have passed, you need to defend against waves of enemies, grow food, build walls, hire troops. Your task is to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/3fd63d15e19b55df12a2875f40bcd402.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=320 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Build and survive</i>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>8 types of buildings</u></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 types of opponents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique graphics style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We alternate between relaxation and tension!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 types of defensive troops</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various resources</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/035ad33fda91d31ca4f4ee7d13742ed8.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=144 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/f272c0a9bf4f8db9c1641b64ab50087c.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=80 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/7f26ea1c17cf272e2961c7f00400b3f4.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immerse</strong> yourself in a <u><strong>fortress building simulator</strong></u> with elements of <u><strong>turn-based strategy</strong></u> and <u><strong>real-time strategy</strong></u> in our new game Tiny Europe! <br> <br><strong>Dark forces do not sleep!</strong> You have miraculously survived on the bizarre continent of Europe, but this is just the beginning. You have to build a fortress in <u><i>60 seconds</i></u>, until the first enemy attack begins. Everything you manage to build in <u><i>60 seconds</i></u> will be free for you. After <u><i>60 seconds</i></u> have passed, you need to defend against waves of enemies, grow food, build walls, hire troops. Your task is to survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/3fd63d15e19b55df12a2875f40bcd402.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=320 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Build and survive</i>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>8 types of buildings</u></strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 types of opponents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique graphics style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We alternate between relaxation and tension!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 types of defensive troops</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various resources</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/035ad33fda91d31ca4f4ee7d13742ed8.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=144 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2497650/extras/f272c0a9bf4f8db9c1641b64ab50087c.avif?t=1753025724\" width=570 height=80 /></span></p>",
